title: Russell Dickerson On The Time He Got Punched in the Face + Underrated 90’s Country Artists + Fun Fact Friday: Actor Who Was Almost Captain America

description:
We talked to Russell Dickerson as he is at the beach to talk about his latest song as well as being a dad, his marriage, and the one time he got punched in the face. We share our picks for the most underrated 90’s country artist. Amy shares her 5 fun facts of the week!
